title: Tiny Home in the Forest!!!
posting_body: ['Live the pristine life in the forest in this cute remodeled tiny home!', 'Fully remodeled turnkey Tiny Home that DRIVES!', 'Even has AC!!!', 'This is a fully liveable 26’ Ford Jamboree remodeled into a tiny home interior last summer:', 'Features:', 'AC', 'Propane Heat', '3 beds', '20 cupboards', 'Generator', 'Brand new on demand water heater', 'New Handcrafted Spruce Dining Table', 'Née Toilet', 'New Faucet', '3 new vents (still in boxes you install when ready, others are working)', 'New Waterproof Flooring', 'New Nontoxic Mineral Paint', 'Portable carport has kept it dry', '7 new custom mirrors for added light', 'New Custom Curtains', 'Extra Sleeping Bag', 'Full Size Real Mattress', 'Marble tile backsplash', 'Full Size Freezer/Fridge', 'Oven', '4 Burner Stove', 'Can tow anything', 'Everything works!', 'This is a steal!', 'Sell by August 1 for move in where is in Glacier and pay $525/mo including all utilities or take it on the road to live the free life!!!', 'Currently on 15 forested acres all hooked up to utilities avail on a monthly lease from the property company.', '90k miles', '$11,999obo - Must sell this week']
